Small hive beetle infestation (_Aethina tumida_), Italy
-------------------------------------------------------
Information received on [and dated] 18 Sep 2014 from Prof Dr Romano Marabelli, Chief Veterinary Officer, Secretary General, Ministry of Health, Rome, Italy

Summary
Report type: immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 5 Sep 2014
Date of pre-confirmation of the event: 12 Sep 2014
Report date: 18 Sep 2014
Date submitted to OIE: 18 Sep 2014
Reason for notification: 1st occurrence of a listed disease
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: _Aethina tumida_
Nature of diagnosis: clinical, laboratory (basic)
This event pertains to the whole country

New outbreaks (2)
Outbreak 1: Gioia Tauro, Reggio Calabria, Calabria
Date of start of the outbreak: 5 Sep 2014
Outbreak status: continuing (or date resolved not provided)
