Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: unknown or inconclusive
Epidemiological comments: _Aethina tumida_ was identified in nuclei located in close proximity of Gioia Tauro's harbour.

Control measures
Measures applied: stamping out; movement control inside the country; screening; zoning; disinfection of infected premises/establishment(s); no vaccination; no treatment of affected animals
Measures to be applied: no other measures.

Diagnostic test results
